With floor-to-ceiling glass walls that invite abundant natural light, the home features an open layout seamlessly connecting indoor and outdoor living spaces. The kitchen, complete with a large island, custom cabinetry, and Viking appliances, is a delight for any home chef. All bedrooms boast spacious closets with custom built-ins and high ceilings. The master bedroom is a luminous retreat with floor-to-ceiling glass sliders providing a scenic view of the expansive yard. Enjoy outdoor living with a large covered patio, built-in BBQ, kitchen area, pool, wood fire pit, and a half-court basketball court. The small studio area beside the garage is another versatile space this home offers. Additionally, there is an outdoor steam shower which adds a touch of luxury. The home is equipped with 2 water heaters. This home is conveniently located near excellent schools, parks, shopping, dining, and more, offering the epitome of Valley living!

3rd Party Synd. Remarks: After a fun day of exploring Wine Country, return home to 2467 Mill Creek Rd. This property exudes serenity & tranquility, offering a much-needed escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Nestled on 28+/- acres, this hacienda-style home is full of charm & character. Its unique architecture is highlighted by a central courtyard, a pool & an outdoor kitchen, perfect for leisurely gatherings & entertaining guests. As you relax by the poolside, you'll be treated to breathtaking views of the surrounding vineyards, creating a picturesque backdrop for your outdoor activities. With ample space available, this property is ideal for those with a passion for animals, farming, & gardening. Whether you dream of having a horse or goats, cultivating crops, a vineyard, or tending to a vibrant garden, the possibilities are endless. Despite its country ambiance, this gem is conveniently located just 5 minutes away from the historic Healdsburg Plaza. This proximity allows you to easily access the charming town's boutiques, restaurants, & cultural attractions. 2467 Mill creek Rd. offers an idyllic lifestyle, blending the best of both worlds: a peaceful retreat surrounded by nature, yet close enough to the vibrant heart of Healdsburg.
